asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Blake the Mamasan
description: Blake, the youngest and sexiest Fluf-In-Charge of the Backalley, the place that is packed with thousands of Izakaya, bars and nightclub etc. It is a place where the Flufs go for nightlife, and finally, for breeding... Before Blake became in charge of Backalley, she was only a pure and innocent girl in the countryside. She felt in love with a good looking cowboy but eventually her heart was broken. She then went to the city and started working in the Backalley. One day she met a mysterious Fluf who was a guest of the bar she worked at. The place was too dark that Blake could not see clearly the face of this mysterious Fluf, but the whistle in the mouth of this Fluf let her recall about her ex. The mysterious Fluf walked closer to Blake and she finally see his nose, his teeth, and his eyes...and then she fainted. When she woke up, she only remembered the last thing she have seen -- two dollor signs. She realized that something has happened to her. She rushed into the washroom, looked into the mirror and found her eyes become Dollor sign. Since then, anything that her eyes looked at will become valuable and profitable. Look at the gold cap she is now wearing is one of the result. She believes that this is a super power that the mysterious Fluf gifted to her. She later called this ability the "Dollar Eye Power". With the Dollor Eye Power, she mastered the Backalley and become the Fluf-In-Charge. Many flufs come to Backalley to have nightlife, to get rich, and finally to breed...Due to her authorities and power, everybody in the alley calls her Blake the Mamasan.
